---
import AppLayout from '../layouts/AppLayout.astro';
---

<AppLayout
  title="Roadmap"
  description="VibeCodingWiki development roadmap and upcoming features"
>
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-5xl">
    <article class="rounded border border-[#a2a9b1] bg-white p-8 shadow-sm">
      <h1 class="mb-4 text-3xl font-semibold text-[#202122]">VibeCodingWiki Roadmap</h1>
      <p class="mb-8 text-sm text-[#54595d]">
        Our vision for the future of VibeCodingWiki. This roadmap outlines the features and improvements we're working on to make the platform better for the VibeCoding community.
      </p>

      <div class="space-y-8">
        <!-- In Progress -->
        <section>
          <h2 class="mb-4 flex items-center gap-2 text-xl font-semibold text-[#202122]">
            <span class="rounded bg-[#0645ad] px-2 py-1 text-xs text-white">In Progress</span>
            Current Development
          </h2>
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div class="rounded border border-[#c8ccd1] bg-[#f8f9fa] p-4">
              <h3 class="mb-2 text-base font-semibold text-[#202122]">üîß Bug Fixes</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-[#54595d]">
                Ongoing work to identify and resolve issues across the platform, improving stability and user experience.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="rounded border border-[#c8ccd1] bg-[#f8f9fa] p-4">
              <h3 class="mb-2 text-base font-semibold text-[#202122]">üì± Mobile View Improvements</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-[#54595d]">
                Enhancing responsive design to ensure VibeCodingWiki works seamlessly across all devices. Currently the mobile experience needs improvement.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Planned -->
        <section>
          <h2 class="mb-4 flex items-center gap-2 text-xl font-semibold text-[#202122]">
            <span class="rounded bg-[#28a745] px-2 py-1 text-xs text-white">Planned</span>
            Upcoming Features
          </h2>
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div class="rounded border border-[#c8ccd1] bg-[#f8f9fa] p-4">
              <h3 class="mb-2 text-base font-semibold text-[#202122]">üîå MCP Integration</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-[#54595d]">
                Integration with Model Context Protocol (MCP) to enhance AI-assisted editing and content generation capabilities.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="rounded border border-[#c8ccd1] bg-[#f8f9fa] p-4">
              <h3 class="mb-2 text-base font-semibold text-[#202122]">‚úçÔ∏è Contribution & Moderation Flow Improvements</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-[#54595d]">
                Streamlining the process for contributors to submit edits and for moderators to review and approve changes. Better diff visualization and conflict resolution.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="rounded border border-[#c8ccd1] bg-[#f8f9fa] p-4">
              <h3 class="mb-2 text-base font-semibold text-[#202122]">üì∞ News Page</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-[#54595d]">
                Dedicated page for VibeCoding community news, updates, and announcements. Keep track of the latest developments in the ecosystem.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="rounded border border-[#c8ccd1] bg-[#f8f9fa] p-4">
              <h3 class="mb-2 text-base font-semibold text-[#202122]">üì± VibeCodingWiki App</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-[#54595d]">
                Native mobile and desktop application for VibeCodingWiki, providing offline access and enhanced editing capabilities.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <!-- How to Contribute -->
        <section class="mt-8 rounded border border-[#0645ad] bg-[#e6f2ff] p-6">
          <h2 class="mb-3 text-lg font-semibold text-[#202122]">Want to help shape the roadmap?</h2>
          <p class="mb-4 text-sm text-[#202122]">
            VibeCodingWiki is built by the community, for the community. We welcome suggestions, feedback, and contributions!
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc space-y-2 pl-5 text-sm text-[#202122]">
            <li>Join the discussion on our community channels</li>
            <li>Submit feature requests through the wiki</li>
            <li>Contribute code or documentation improvements</li>
            <li>Help moderate and curate content</li>
          </ul>
        </section>
      </div>
    </article>
  </div>
</AppLayout>
